# Frontend Environment Variables

# Backend API URL
# Set this to your backend API endpoint
# 
# TESTING WITHOUT BACKEND (uses mock data - perfect for UI development):
# Leave this commented out or set to invalid URL to test with mock data
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://mock-data
#
# For local development with Railway backend:
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://supervisortasks-production.up.railway.app
#
# For local development with local backend:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
#
# For production deployment (Vercel):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://supervisortasks-production.up.railway.app
#
# NOTE: If backend is unavailable, the app automatically falls back to mock data
# See TESTING.md for comprehensive testing guide
